WEBVTT

01:50.070 --> 01:53.960
[Love Between Lines]

01:54.270 --> 01:56.860
[Episode 6]

01:58.150 --> 01:58.750
Slow down.

01:58.840 --> 01:59.440
Slow down.

02:02.840 --> 02:03.450
I...

02:04.260 --> 02:04.950
I...

02:05.550 --> 02:06.160
I...

02:07.960 --> 02:09.330
D-Don't throw up on me.

02:16.190 --> 02:18.050
Why do you have the key to my house?

02:21.320 --> 02:22.510
Come on, come on.

02:22.930 --> 02:23.420
Come on.

02:29.530 --> 02:31.180
Up there is...

02:31.210 --> 02:32.310
They're sleeping. Be quiet.

02:32.310 --> 02:32.970
My house...

02:38.590 --> 02:39.390
Open the door.

02:40.380 --> 02:41.579
Did you bring the key?

02:51.550 --> 02:52.320
Take it.

03:10.880 --> 03:11.630
Mr. Xiao.

03:13.520 --> 03:15.390
I'd rather lose

03:15.700 --> 03:17.579
than run away.

04:30.540 --> 04:31.980
Why am I here?

04:55.510 --> 04:56.150
Hu Xiu,

04:56.430 --> 04:57.240
is that you?

04:58.830 --> 04:59.870
Yes, it's me.

05:00.040 --> 05:01.120
I'm sorry. I...

05:01.140 --> 05:02.700
I don't know why I'm here.

05:02.730 --> 05:03.680
I remember I had a meal

05:03.680 --> 05:04.770
and drank some wine,

05:04.770 --> 05:07.460
and suddenly showed up here.

05:07.710 --> 05:08.510
I know.

05:10.060 --> 05:11.690
You know I'm here?

05:12.300 --> 05:13.500
That's not the point.

05:13.660 --> 05:15.740
Then what is the point? I...

05:16.370 --> 05:19.030
The point is that the lock
of the attic is broken.

05:21.420 --> 05:23.550
Why did you lock the door for no reason?

05:27.020 --> 05:29.000
You were not trying to keep me out,
were you?

05:29.000 --> 05:31.250
Do you have any idea
what you're like when you're drunk?

05:31.250 --> 05:34.580
I still wouldn't barge into someone else's
room on purpose.

05:34.750 --> 05:35.370
I don't care.

05:35.370 --> 05:37.210
Get this door unlocked right now.

05:37.210 --> 05:37.980
What time do you think it is now?

05:37.980 --> 05:40.210
Where am I supposed
to find a locksmith for you?

05:40.210 --> 05:41.060
I'm thirsty.

05:41.980 --> 05:43.890
I can't even get water in to you.

05:52.740 --> 05:53.250
Thanks.

05:54.659 --> 05:55.590
You're welcome.

05:56.300 --> 05:56.940
Mr. Xiao.

05:57.420 --> 05:58.860
It's so late. Are you

05:58.980 --> 06:00.740
still up, or did you

06:01.130 --> 06:01.940
just wake up?

06:02.450 --> 06:03.130
Still up.

06:04.010 --> 06:06.010
Not comfortable staying in the attic?

06:06.010 --> 06:07.300
No. Just working.

06:07.890 --> 06:09.010
So dedicated.

06:10.210 --> 06:13.010
You were busy with the Lyman project,
weren't you?

06:14.010 --> 06:14.740
Mr. Xiao,

06:14.940 --> 06:16.500
you moved into this lane

06:16.580 --> 06:19.110
because of the Lyman's
project competition?

06:20.450 --> 06:21.420
But I heard

06:21.570 --> 06:23.810
Zhuling will also participate
in the competition.

06:23.810 --> 06:24.660
So what?

06:25.300 --> 06:27.030
You think I'll lose to Zhuling?

06:27.060 --> 06:28.540
Of course not.

06:29.250 --> 06:30.180
I believe

06:30.180 --> 06:32.090
Dynamism won't lose.

06:32.130 --> 06:32.730
Why?

06:33.760 --> 06:35.330
It's only your first day on the job.

06:35.330 --> 06:36.980
What's wrong with my first day?

06:36.980 --> 06:37.620
I've been following

06:37.620 --> 06:38.330
Dynamism

06:38.330 --> 06:39.250
for 3 years.

06:39.250 --> 06:40.659
My knowledge about it

06:40.940 --> 06:42.800
is only slightly less than yours,

06:42.810 --> 06:44.890
despite your position as founder.

06:49.060 --> 06:51.060
Why did you suddenly drink tonight?

06:53.180 --> 06:55.870
I wanted to apologize.

06:57.210 --> 06:57.940
Apologize?

06:58.210 --> 06:59.409
What did you do wrong?

07:03.100 --> 07:03.940
If you can't even say

07:03.940 --> 07:04.890
what you did wrong,

07:04.890 --> 07:06.750
then why do you need to apologize?

07:07.230 --> 07:09.160
I just felt I should make a gesture.

07:10.010 --> 07:12.180
After all, I was too outspoken before

07:12.180 --> 07:13.250
and said many

07:13.540 --> 07:14.740
thoughtless things.

07:16.330 --> 07:19.190
And I misunderstood
that you blocked my interview.

07:21.720 --> 07:22.700
If you put it that way,

07:22.700 --> 07:24.300
then I should apologize too.

07:24.980 --> 07:26.740
The day we signed the leasing contract,

07:26.740 --> 07:29.140
I originally wanted
to give you a heads-up.

07:29.370 --> 07:30.620
Because this job

07:31.000 --> 07:33.400
isn't any easier
than being a GM assistant.

07:34.100 --> 07:35.100
Moreover, your family

07:35.100 --> 07:36.740
doesn't even know about your decision.

07:36.740 --> 07:37.800
That's definitely

07:37.909 --> 07:39.770
trouble from both inside and out.

07:41.850 --> 07:44.650
Then why did you pass me in the interview?

07:51.620 --> 07:53.659
Was it because of
our landlord-tenant relationship

07:53.659 --> 07:55.190
that you gave me a shortcut?

07:55.770 --> 07:57.370
After hearing all my stories

07:57.570 --> 07:59.690
about setbacks, regrets, and failures,

07:59.690 --> 08:00.420
did you think

08:00.740 --> 08:01.620
I was particularly miserable?

08:01.620 --> 08:03.280
So you gave me the green light?

08:06.370 --> 08:07.770
It was indeed a shortcut.

08:10.690 --> 08:12.750
But what this shortcut didn't show me

08:13.300 --> 08:14.960
what you said about setbacks,

08:15.010 --> 08:15.660
regrets,

08:15.980 --> 08:16.710
or failures.

08:18.010 --> 08:19.410
Then what did it show you?

08:21.060 --> 08:21.890
Potential.

08:22.890 --> 08:27.440
♪ Close your eyes for me ♪

08:28.970 --> 08:31.030
♪ Don't rush to wake up ♪

08:30.770 --> 08:32.850
You saw
my college sketch design portfolio?

08:31.330 --> 08:34.440
♪ Before the night ends ♪

08:34.490 --> 08:36.220
And you think it's pretty good?

08:37.630 --> 08:42.940
♪ Will you stay with me? ♪

08:39.380 --> 08:41.049
But those are all past works.

08:41.940 --> 08:42.490
Hu Xiu.

08:43.059 --> 08:43.970
When day breaks,

08:43.860 --> 08:45.860
♪ I won't search for ♪

08:44.460 --> 08:46.460
don't think about the past anymore.

08:46.660 --> 08:49.470
♪ The reason we met ♪

08:47.330 --> 08:48.810
Our only goal now

08:49.300 --> 08:50.990
is Lyman's competition project.

08:50.990 --> 08:56.520
♪ The city gradually turns pale
outside the window ♪

08:54.900 --> 08:55.540
Mr. Xiao.

08:56.300 --> 08:57.090
Then in exchange,

08:57.090 --> 08:59.180
can you show me your design draft?

08:58.400 --> 09:00.520
♪ The stars twinkle ♪

08:59.180 --> 09:00.810
Any design draft will do.

09:00.940 --> 09:02.690
The one for the Galaxy Bookstore
is fine too.

09:01.510 --> 09:05.520
♪ I've quieted down ♪

09:03.260 --> 09:05.020
Or the one for that teahouse in Suzhou.

09:05.020 --> 09:06.780
Or the one for the café
on Jianguo West Road.

09:06.780 --> 09:07.260
Any of them will do.

09:07.250 --> 09:10.450
♪ What kind of story will you like? ♪

09:07.260 --> 09:07.850
Anything works.

09:07.850 --> 09:09.250
I just want to take a look.

09:09.540 --> 09:11.540
After all, those who are close
have the advantage.

09:10.570 --> 09:12.230
♪ Would you join me? ♪

09:11.540 --> 09:13.540
Look, we're about

09:12.250 --> 09:16.020
♪ To make a long, romantic dream ♪

09:13.690 --> 09:14.690
2 meters away now.

09:14.900 --> 09:15.540
Mr. Xiao.

09:16.740 --> 09:19.310
♪ Just you and me ♪

09:20.490 --> 09:21.330
Mr. Xiao.

09:21.930 --> 09:24.120
♪ Briefly, beyond the clamor ♪

09:24.140 --> 09:26.050
♪ Getting closer to you secretly ♪

09:26.070 --> 09:29.920
♪ Clinging to that trace of unknown joy ♪

09:30.310 --> 09:34.320
♪ Oh, special night ♪

09:36.690 --> 09:38.300
I'll send the drafts to you
when I get to work.

09:37.550 --> 09:41.820
♪ We will meet tomorrow ♪

09:43.060 --> 09:44.670
♪ I know ♪

09:45.010 --> 09:49.070
♪ Oh, special night ♪

09:50.490 --> 09:51.490
It's getting late.

09:51.490 --> 09:52.430
You should get some rest.

09:52.430 --> 09:56.520
♪ Oh, special night ♪

09:54.140 --> 09:54.800
Good night.

10:07.940 --> 10:08.730
Thank you, Sir.

10:08.730 --> 10:09.420
No problem.

10:09.420 --> 10:10.420
Sorry to bother you so early.

10:10.420 --> 10:11.420
Alright, goodbye.

10:11.420 --> 10:12.020
Goodbye.

10:13.090 --> 10:14.490
Oh no, I'm late.

10:14.490 --> 10:15.450
What's the rush?

10:16.450 --> 10:17.060
You're the boss.

10:17.060 --> 10:17.900
You don't need to clock in.

10:17.900 --> 10:18.970
Of course, you're not worried.

10:18.970 --> 10:20.850
Let's grab breakfast
at the lane entrance first.

10:20.850 --> 10:22.650
Then you can ride with me to work.

10:32.060 --> 10:33.120
What are you doing?

10:36.450 --> 10:39.020
That was our colleague
from the studio just now, right?

10:39.020 --> 10:40.140
It's not good to be seen.

10:40.140 --> 10:42.670
They might misunderstand our relationship.

10:43.300 --> 10:45.330
I haven't accomplished anything yet.

10:45.330 --> 10:47.970
If people say I got the job
through the back door,

10:47.970 --> 10:49.970
I wouldn't be able to defend myself.

10:50.450 --> 10:52.180
Drive to the back of the studio,

10:52.180 --> 10:53.440
and I'll get out there.

11:03.400 --> 11:06.930
Do I look like someone
who would give people special treatment?

11:10.570 --> 11:12.450
Mr. Xiao, remember to get out later.

11:12.450 --> 11:13.490
I'm going first.

11:31.810 --> 11:32.370
Mr. Xiao,

11:32.390 --> 11:34.320
didn't you say you'd get off later?

11:34.810 --> 11:36.450
I didn't do anything wrong.

11:43.920 --> 11:44.800
Have you seen?

11:44.900 --> 11:45.540
Yes.

11:45.540 --> 11:46.490
Is it true?

11:46.490 --> 11:48.090
Did Mr. Xiao really say that?

11:48.190 --> 11:49.260
Is that the point?

11:49.290 --> 11:51.820
The point should be
who the whistleblower is.

11:53.830 --> 11:54.420
Look.

11:56.070 --> 11:58.470
[Xinrui Design Chases Fame:
Newbie Xiao Zhiyu Sparks Controversy]

12:09.300 --> 12:12.030
Lyman has disqualified us
from the competition.

12:13.450 --> 12:15.930
Sun Daqin is in charge of
this project competition.

12:15.930 --> 12:17.790
Have you been able to contact him?

12:18.730 --> 12:20.690
I've called Mr. Sun several times,

12:20.730 --> 12:22.060
but he's not answering.

12:23.420 --> 12:24.300
Logically speaking,

12:24.300 --> 12:25.810
even if there had been a debate
about those words,

12:25.810 --> 12:27.810
they never would have caused a stir.

12:27.850 --> 12:29.540
But shortly after this news was released,

12:29.540 --> 12:31.900
a bunch of industry insiders
rushed in to discuss it.

12:31.900 --> 12:33.180
The strangest thing is,

12:33.180 --> 12:35.020
it's been brewing for a short while,

12:35.020 --> 12:38.480
and Lyman has directly disqualified us
from the competition.

12:38.690 --> 12:41.380
This news is deliberately targeted
at this competition.

12:41.380 --> 12:43.850
Public opinion is just an excuse
for the disqualification.

12:43.850 --> 12:46.380
Someone must be pulling strings
behind this.

12:50.900 --> 12:52.090
You mean

12:52.490 --> 12:54.660
someone deliberately wants
to sabotage our participation?

12:54.660 --> 12:55.520
Who could it be?

12:57.180 --> 12:58.450
If Dynamism is out,

12:58.450 --> 12:59.260
whoever benefits

12:59.260 --> 13:00.990
is naturally the one behind it.

13:03.450 --> 13:04.090
Well,

13:04.940 --> 13:07.170
I'll first activate our PR emergency plan

13:07.170 --> 13:09.030
to suppress the media attention.

13:09.300 --> 13:10.660
As for Mr. Sun at Lyman,

13:10.730 --> 13:12.050
I'll figure something out.

13:12.050 --> 13:13.290
For this matter,

13:13.320 --> 13:15.340
no matter how many complications
are behind it,

13:15.340 --> 13:17.470
you should focus on your design first.

13:25.300 --> 13:26.780
Our company doesn't have

13:26.780 --> 13:27.710
many employees.

13:27.780 --> 13:29.020
Do you have any idea

13:29.330 --> 13:30.930
who leaked the information?

13:33.240 --> 13:33.970
Don't worry.

13:35.970 --> 13:38.300
This person will expose themselves soon.

13:46.170 --> 13:47.850
Mr. Pei, your tea ceremony skills

13:47.850 --> 13:49.490
are improving day by day.

13:49.800 --> 13:50.660
You flatter me.

13:52.140 --> 13:53.340
Thank you. Thank you.

13:54.100 --> 13:54.900
Please try it.

13:55.090 --> 13:55.690
Thank you.

13:58.570 --> 13:59.540
For this matter,

14:00.340 --> 14:01.600
I owe you a lot, Mr. Sun.

14:01.910 --> 14:03.490
Mr. Pei, you're being too polite.

14:03.490 --> 14:04.610
It was nothing.

14:05.690 --> 14:07.450
Think about your relationship
with Mr. Xie.

14:07.450 --> 14:08.860
Like father and son.

14:09.070 --> 14:11.590
These are just formalities.

14:11.970 --> 14:13.060
That may be true,

14:13.260 --> 14:15.850
but I don't want to put Uncle Xie
in a difficult position.

14:15.850 --> 14:16.570
Mr. Sun,

14:17.300 --> 14:18.660
what if someone

14:18.660 --> 14:19.690
goes to Uncle Xie

14:19.690 --> 14:20.820
to plead their case?

14:21.460 --> 14:23.120
What should Uncle Xie do then?

14:23.330 --> 14:24.460
They wouldn't dare.

14:25.140 --> 14:26.380
As you know,

14:26.860 --> 14:28.770
he lives in seclusion,

14:29.170 --> 14:31.690
and I handle all his daily affairs.

14:32.260 --> 14:34.770
If anyone with ill intentions

14:34.790 --> 14:36.310
wants to bother Mr. Xie,

14:36.690 --> 14:38.570
they'll have to get past me first.

14:39.940 --> 14:40.810
Rest assured.

14:42.170 --> 14:42.970
Have some tea.

14:50.300 --> 14:51.900
Mr. Pei, everything is done.

14:51.940 --> 14:53.540
When can I start working?

14:58.170 --> 14:59.640
This is the optimized profile.

14:59.640 --> 15:00.700
Please take a look.

15:02.190 --> 15:04.020
It's good overall, but

15:04.050 --> 15:06.430
there are a few points
that need attention.

15:06.430 --> 15:07.450
[Mom]

15:12.660 --> 15:13.750
I need to take this call.

15:13.750 --> 15:15.480
You can go ahead with your work.

15:26.260 --> 15:26.940
Zhiyu,

15:27.690 --> 15:29.330
am I interrupting you?

15:30.740 --> 15:31.290
No.

15:32.150 --> 15:33.350
It must be late there.

15:33.940 --> 15:35.200
Did something happen?

15:35.750 --> 15:36.460
Nothing.

15:37.030 --> 15:38.760
Your uncle and I are doing fine.

15:40.450 --> 15:41.300
Um...

15:41.680 --> 15:43.890
I saw the news online.

15:44.300 --> 15:45.380
Are you okay?

15:46.450 --> 15:47.100
I'm fine.

15:47.710 --> 15:49.990
You should still be careful at work.

15:50.970 --> 15:52.430
Even when problems arise,

15:52.540 --> 15:53.610
stay calm.

15:54.060 --> 15:55.790
Don't act like your father did.

16:00.730 --> 16:01.460
Don't worry.

16:01.540 --> 16:03.260
I'll properly handle my own affairs.

16:03.260 --> 16:04.140
That's good.

16:05.210 --> 16:05.850
By the way,

16:06.090 --> 16:08.150
after my discussion with your uncle,

16:08.570 --> 16:10.450
we've decided to return to
Shanghai this year

16:10.450 --> 16:12.020
and stay for a while.

16:12.180 --> 16:12.900
This way,

16:13.210 --> 16:14.330
our family

16:14.370 --> 16:15.960
can reunite soon.

16:17.090 --> 16:17.900
Got it.

16:18.660 --> 16:19.320
Hanging up.

16:26.690 --> 16:27.260
Sun.

16:27.580 --> 16:28.310
I'm leaving.

16:28.330 --> 16:29.390
I'll be off in a sec.

16:29.490 --> 16:31.090
Has he already left work?

16:38.450 --> 16:39.780
Xiu, are you off work yet?

16:39.780 --> 16:41.490
I'm running errands near your studio.

16:41.490 --> 16:43.090
Let's have dinner together.

17:11.339 --> 17:13.339
I heard someone fell from upstairs.

17:13.859 --> 17:15.990
I think it's the architect of this gym.

17:16.480 --> 17:17.770
It must be suicide.

17:19.290 --> 17:19.970
Jerk!

17:20.319 --> 17:21.910
Suicide is too easy for you!

17:22.690 --> 17:24.619
Don't think you don't have to
take responsibility this way!

17:24.619 --> 17:26.730
That consent form
couldn't have been signed by my father.

17:26.730 --> 17:28.660
The gym collapse wasn't his fault.

17:29.530 --> 17:31.140
Is there nothing I can do?

17:31.580 --> 17:33.410
There's one thing you can do.

17:34.530 --> 17:35.530
Grow up well.

17:36.230 --> 17:37.360
When you come of age,

17:37.690 --> 17:39.780
and when you have the ability
and resources,

17:39.780 --> 17:41.730
you'll have the chance to unravel

17:42.270 --> 17:43.600
and discover the truth.

17:47.360 --> 17:48.360
Time to clear out!

17:48.530 --> 17:49.860
Is anyone still inside?

18:01.610 --> 18:02.570
You know what,

18:02.590 --> 18:04.720
the canteen in your park is quite good.

18:05.360 --> 18:07.690
Guangming can get food
even when working overtime.

18:07.690 --> 18:09.140
You bought this for him, right?

18:09.140 --> 18:11.000
He's been working so hard lately.

18:11.450 --> 18:12.940
One project just finished,

18:12.940 --> 18:14.100
and now he's busy again.

18:14.100 --> 18:16.560
He doesn't give himself
any breathing room.

18:16.690 --> 18:18.420
He's famous for being intense.

18:18.530 --> 18:20.620
Even though I
wasn't in the same department as him,

18:20.620 --> 18:22.350
I've heard of his name long ago.

18:22.530 --> 18:24.180
I know he works very hard.

18:25.010 --> 18:26.690
He seems strange lately.

18:26.970 --> 18:28.430
I can't put my finger on it.

18:29.690 --> 18:30.140
You...

18:31.420 --> 18:32.220
Wait for a sec.

18:33.490 --> 18:34.290
What's wrong?

18:35.450 --> 18:37.450
Something happened in the company.

18:40.760 --> 18:42.820
Don't worry. I'll call a taxi for you.

18:57.530 --> 18:59.140
He's really calm about this.

19:29.580 --> 19:30.210
Zhou,

19:30.770 --> 19:31.940
proceed with the Lyman proposal

19:31.940 --> 19:32.970
as planned.

19:33.210 --> 19:33.770
Ms. Zhou.

19:34.820 --> 19:37.340
Actually, besides Lyman,

19:37.450 --> 19:38.730
we have other projects.

19:38.730 --> 19:40.050
Since we've been disqualified,

19:40.050 --> 19:41.510
isn't it more appropriate

19:41.590 --> 19:43.900
for us to focus our energy

19:43.930 --> 19:44.990
on other projects?

19:45.940 --> 19:46.900
Yeah, Ms. Zhou.

19:47.050 --> 19:48.210
What if

19:48.490 --> 19:50.620
we lose sight of other opportunities?

19:51.770 --> 19:52.420
Everyone,

19:52.730 --> 19:53.770
during our last dinner,

19:53.770 --> 19:55.010
we just talked about

19:55.010 --> 19:56.140
making sure our ongoing projects

19:56.140 --> 19:57.270
have good outcomes.

19:57.490 --> 19:59.020
This is just the beginning.

19:59.250 --> 20:00.340
It's a small setback,

20:00.340 --> 20:02.270
and you're already falling apart?

20:09.140 --> 20:09.770
Ms. Zhou,

20:10.580 --> 20:12.690
this is the assignment
Mr. Xiao gave earlier.

20:12.690 --> 20:13.420
I've compiled all the ideas

20:13.420 --> 20:15.080
regarding the Lyman project.

20:15.450 --> 20:17.140
I'm not quite sure
about the courtyard garden part yet.

20:17.140 --> 20:18.540
Everything else is done.

20:18.860 --> 20:20.620
I see Mr. Xiao hasn't arrived today.

20:20.620 --> 20:22.550
Would you mind taking a look first?

20:26.620 --> 20:27.820
Come with me to Lyman.

20:38.050 --> 20:38.730
Ms. Zhou,

20:39.010 --> 20:40.670
isn't Mr. Xiao coming with us?

20:40.990 --> 20:42.800
He'll meet us directly at Lyman.

21:05.250 --> 21:05.860
Ms. Zhou.

21:06.490 --> 21:07.090
He's here.

21:07.860 --> 21:08.590
You're here.

21:10.820 --> 21:11.420
Hello.

21:11.620 --> 21:12.770
I'm Zhou Yan from Dynamism.

21:12.770 --> 21:14.580
I have an appointment
with Mr. Sun from your company.

21:14.580 --> 21:15.780
Please wait a moment.

21:17.010 --> 21:18.010
Please follow me.

21:23.340 --> 21:23.830
Okay.

21:25.110 --> 21:26.730
[Lyman Group]

21:27.260 --> 21:28.930
Mr. Sun is still in a meeting.

21:29.450 --> 21:30.770
Please wait a moment.

21:31.340 --> 21:31.940
Thank you.

21:32.250 --> 21:33.180
You're welcome.

21:36.450 --> 21:38.380
What did Sun Daqin say on the phone?

21:39.650 --> 21:40.840
He didn't say anything,

21:40.840 --> 21:42.500
just beating around the bush.

21:45.180 --> 21:47.290
I felt this couldn't continue.

21:47.290 --> 21:48.690
So I arranged to meet him.

21:48.770 --> 21:50.340
He agreed quite readily.

21:51.690 --> 21:53.620
Does that mean there's still hope?

21:55.260 --> 21:57.520
It depends on how the conversation goes.

22:19.530 --> 22:20.380
Hu Xiu, go ask again

22:20.380 --> 22:21.710
what's really going on.

22:21.850 --> 22:23.110
No need to ask anymore.

22:23.250 --> 22:23.820
Let's go.

22:25.420 --> 22:26.450
Why don't we wait a little longer?

22:26.450 --> 22:28.450
Maybe something has held him up.

22:29.250 --> 22:31.690
Mr. Sun never intended to meet with us.

22:35.100 --> 22:35.940
I'll contact He

22:35.940 --> 22:37.870
and ask him to bring the car around.

22:42.900 --> 22:43.580
I'm sorry.

22:44.050 --> 22:45.860
I made things seem too simple.

22:46.940 --> 22:49.150
I promised you could focus on design,

22:49.250 --> 22:49.980
but instead,

22:50.290 --> 22:51.580
I dragged you here

22:51.610 --> 22:53.270
only to get the cold shoulder.

22:53.490 --> 22:54.750
This isn't your fault.

22:54.900 --> 22:55.630
Don't worry,

22:55.640 --> 22:57.170
I'll figure something out.

23:03.860 --> 23:05.460
Why did you bring Hu Xiu here?

23:07.100 --> 23:07.900
You know what,

23:08.490 --> 23:09.950
that girl is quite clever.

23:10.210 --> 23:11.060
And

23:11.680 --> 23:12.810
she works very hard.

23:14.010 --> 23:15.450
This is the assignment you gave her

23:15.450 --> 23:16.770
on her first day.

23:16.980 --> 23:18.100
After just a few days,

23:18.100 --> 23:20.030
she completed it remarkably well.

23:29.530 --> 23:31.730
I have something to attend to,
so I'll go first.

23:31.730 --> 23:32.260
Mr. Xiao,

23:32.360 --> 23:33.370
would you mind

23:33.390 --> 23:34.520
giving Hu Xiu a ride?

23:35.450 --> 23:38.010
Just drop me off
at the nearest subway station.

23:38.010 --> 23:38.610
Thank you.

23:39.290 --> 23:39.770
Bye.

23:43.250 --> 23:43.780
Let's go.

23:58.530 --> 23:59.340
Let me tell you,

23:59.340 --> 24:00.900
I rarely get a day off.

24:01.450 --> 24:02.510
Who is that person?

24:04.310 --> 24:05.580
Sun Daqin from Lyman.

24:07.300 --> 24:08.630
Let's meet another day.

24:08.830 --> 24:09.420
Alright.

24:25.620 --> 24:26.250
Mr. Xiao,

24:26.860 --> 24:29.170
are you coming back
to the lane for dinner tonight?

24:29.170 --> 24:30.930
I know a really good restaurant.

24:30.930 --> 24:31.790
I'm not hungry.

24:38.100 --> 24:39.830
The weather is getting cooler.

24:39.960 --> 24:41.810
Is everything okay with your place?

24:41.810 --> 24:42.400
Yeah.

24:50.530 --> 24:52.210
Celebrity architects like him

24:52.210 --> 24:53.340
rely on marketing

24:53.340 --> 24:55.340
rather than solid professional skills.

24:55.340 --> 24:57.050
They use their popularity to get projects

24:57.050 --> 24:59.380
and squeeze out traditional architects.

24:59.660 --> 25:00.620
Just for popularity,

25:00.620 --> 25:02.490
turning architecture
into mere photo backdrops

25:02.490 --> 25:03.490
is truly
putting the cart before the horse.

25:03.490 --> 25:04.950
Do you have plans tonight?

25:06.250 --> 25:06.970
No.

25:07.530 --> 25:08.860
Come with me somewhere.

25:19.490 --> 25:20.100
Mr. Xiao.

25:20.380 --> 25:21.210
She's with me.

25:21.280 --> 25:22.480
Okay. Please come in.

25:30.530 --> 25:31.990
I have a business meeting.

25:32.460 --> 25:33.730
Go wait for me over there.

25:33.730 --> 25:35.710
You can order whatever drink you want.

25:35.710 --> 25:36.640
Except alcohol.

25:37.940 --> 25:38.800
Put it on my tab.

25:52.480 --> 25:54.480
Hello, what would you like to drink?

26:08.180 --> 26:08.940
Sparkling water.

26:08.940 --> 26:10.470
Okay, please wait a moment.

26:24.660 --> 26:25.290
Mr. Xiao,

26:25.660 --> 26:26.340
I'm sorry

26:26.900 --> 26:27.760
for being late.

26:27.890 --> 26:28.540
It's fine.

26:28.690 --> 26:30.250
I know you've been busy these days,
Mr. Wang.

26:30.250 --> 26:31.450
Have you set the date?

26:32.730 --> 26:33.590
This Saturday.

26:33.730 --> 26:35.380
You're our VIP guest.

26:35.380 --> 26:36.640
We need your presence.

26:36.690 --> 26:37.300
Of course.

26:41.300 --> 26:42.060
Mr. Xiao,

26:42.340 --> 26:44.250
you rarely attend social gatherings,

26:44.250 --> 26:45.910
but you specifically asked me out today.

26:45.910 --> 26:48.710
I assume it's not just for small talk.

26:51.490 --> 26:53.090
Indeed, I have a favor to ask.

26:53.690 --> 26:54.940
For the weekend wedding,

26:54.940 --> 26:55.770
I would like to ask you

26:55.770 --> 26:57.370
to invite Mr. Xie from Lyman.

27:05.540 --> 27:06.600
What are you doing?

27:07.690 --> 27:08.690
Fighting online.

27:08.730 --> 27:09.620
I can't stand watching

27:09.620 --> 27:11.530
these people
making something out of nothing.

27:11.530 --> 27:12.970
I have to step in myself.

27:15.530 --> 27:16.420
Let me see

27:16.660 --> 27:19.190
how they're making
these false accusations.

27:33.620 --> 27:34.820
You made good points.

27:35.140 --> 27:36.210
It's useless, though.

27:36.210 --> 27:38.010
My posts are all getting buried.

27:38.260 --> 27:39.660
Don't waste your energy.

27:39.660 --> 27:40.530
No way.

27:41.170 --> 27:42.830
This kind of pathetic framing

27:42.840 --> 27:45.010
is full of obvious holes
to anyone with eyes.

27:45.010 --> 27:45.860
I've been thinking these...

27:45.860 --> 27:46.690
I said it.

27:52.860 --> 27:53.720
That statement

27:54.450 --> 27:55.250
was from me.

27:56.210 --> 27:57.380
W-Why?

27:58.380 --> 27:59.970
H-How did you

28:00.250 --> 28:01.310
-say...
-Let's go.

28:12.290 --> 28:12.820
Mr. Xiao,

28:12.860 --> 28:15.790
would you like me
to call a designated driver for you?

28:16.250 --> 28:17.340
Goodbye, Mr. Xiao.

28:18.180 --> 28:19.780
Aren't we leaving together?

28:20.210 --> 28:21.740
I'll just get a taxi myself.

28:22.180 --> 28:23.980
Then who's going to drive for me?

28:27.050 --> 28:28.910
No wonder you didn't let me drink.

28:30.000 --> 28:30.640
What?

28:34.130 --> 28:34.850
Nothing.

28:35.100 --> 28:35.760
I can drive.

28:58.140 --> 28:58.690
Xiaorou.

28:59.130 --> 29:00.860
Zhan Jie, are you at the office?

29:01.540 --> 29:02.100
I am.

29:02.140 --> 29:02.940
What's wrong?

29:03.660 --> 29:05.540
I've been texting Wang all evening.

29:05.540 --> 29:06.470
I can't find him.

29:06.470 --> 29:07.710
He's not responding.

29:09.010 --> 29:10.210
It's okay, Xiaorou.

29:10.450 --> 29:12.450
He's working overtime at the office.

29:12.450 --> 29:13.860
Probably busy coding.

29:13.890 --> 29:15.340
He might not have noticed his phone.

29:15.340 --> 29:17.340
I came out to buy late-night snacks.

29:17.340 --> 29:18.720
I'll tell him when I get back.

29:18.720 --> 29:19.480
Don't worry.

29:20.090 --> 29:21.620
Okay, thanks for your help.

29:22.540 --> 29:23.100
Miss.

29:23.970 --> 29:25.380
There's traffic ahead.

29:25.400 --> 29:27.490
Would it be convenient
for you to get off here?

29:27.490 --> 29:30.420
It's only a few hundred meters
to your neighborhood.

29:31.250 --> 29:31.900
Alright.

29:32.580 --> 29:33.290
Thank you.

29:33.460 --> 29:35.190
No problem. I've already paid.

29:35.210 --> 29:35.730
Okay.

29:39.210 --> 29:40.140
Zhan Jie?

29:40.140 --> 29:40.880
Thank you, Sir.

29:40.880 --> 29:43.740
Didn't he say he was working overtime
at the office?

30:17.290 --> 30:18.100
Xiaorou?

30:18.600 --> 30:19.930
What are you doing here?

30:22.450 --> 30:23.450
Take me upstairs.

30:23.890 --> 30:25.290
Wang is upstairs, right?

30:25.300 --> 30:25.860
My place

30:25.880 --> 30:27.030
is really messy.

30:27.230 --> 30:28.760
It's not convenient today.

30:31.140 --> 30:32.620
Since when did you

30:32.900 --> 30:34.420
move near our place?

30:35.970 --> 30:36.770
Just moved in.

30:36.900 --> 30:37.450
I...

30:37.860 --> 30:38.490
Fine,

30:39.010 --> 30:40.140
I'll go up by myself.

30:42.040 --> 30:42.570
Xiaorou!

30:45.730 --> 30:46.930
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

30:47.900 --> 30:48.530
Xiaorou!

31:04.050 --> 31:04.690
Done!

31:07.100 --> 31:07.900
Xiaorou.

31:12.290 --> 31:13.530
The first one in so many days.

31:13.530 --> 31:14.770
We can all testify to that.

31:14.770 --> 31:15.490
Yes, that's right.

31:15.490 --> 31:17.890
-The first one.
-Definitely the first one.

31:26.210 --> 31:27.580
So you've been

31:27.610 --> 31:29.070
busy with all this lately?

31:34.490 --> 31:37.140
Why didn't you tell me you quit your job?

31:40.020 --> 31:41.890
You weren't laid off, were you?

31:47.280 --> 31:48.440
Don't laugh.

31:48.690 --> 31:50.290
Were you really laid off?

31:50.800 --> 31:52.040
I wasn't laid off.

31:53.100 --> 31:54.500
And I didn't quit either.

31:56.530 --> 31:58.530
We are planning to start a business.

31:58.900 --> 32:00.210
I didn't tell you before

32:00.210 --> 32:02.270
because things weren't on track yet.

32:02.620 --> 32:04.080
I didn't want you to worry.

32:05.420 --> 32:06.380
Since you didn't quit,

32:06.380 --> 32:08.820
why do you start a business
when everything's going fine?

32:08.820 --> 32:09.580
Many technical staff

32:09.580 --> 32:11.860
eventually moved into management roles.

32:11.860 --> 32:14.320
Although our company offers good benefits,

32:14.360 --> 32:15.260
there's basically no hope

32:15.260 --> 32:16.790
for me to switch positions.

32:17.220 --> 32:18.800
I don't want to travel all the time,

32:18.800 --> 32:20.530
constantly on business trips,

32:20.770 --> 32:22.230
leaving you to live alone.

32:31.210 --> 32:32.340
I've made up my mind.

32:32.620 --> 32:33.860
If you really want to start a business,

32:33.860 --> 32:35.010
just quit your job

32:35.210 --> 32:35.820
and focus on it.

32:35.820 --> 32:36.530
I support you.

32:36.530 --> 32:37.770
I can't quit my job.

32:39.100 --> 32:39.950
If I can earn extra money,

32:39.950 --> 32:41.350
why should I give that up?

32:43.380 --> 32:44.690
We still need to get a new house.

32:44.690 --> 32:45.820
Have you forgotten?

32:45.860 --> 32:47.050
I have a card.

32:47.970 --> 32:49.820
Since the café started making a profit,

32:49.820 --> 32:50.620
I've saved all the money

32:50.620 --> 32:51.730
you've given me.

32:52.100 --> 32:52.860
Take it and use it.

32:52.860 --> 32:53.970
Consider it my investment,

32:53.970 --> 32:54.450
okay?

32:54.450 --> 32:55.180
No way.

32:55.530 --> 32:56.820
I already have money.

32:56.970 --> 32:58.180
Honey,

32:58.900 --> 32:59.660
listen to me.

33:01.900 --> 33:03.100
Our current life

33:03.100 --> 33:04.700
is already satisfying to me.

33:05.660 --> 33:06.380
As for money,

33:06.380 --> 33:07.780
we can earn it gradually.

33:08.250 --> 33:09.490
We'll get a bigger house

33:09.490 --> 33:10.660
sooner or later.

33:11.620 --> 33:12.730
Don't worry.

33:13.180 --> 33:14.460
Don't feel pressured.

33:15.250 --> 33:16.290
I believe our life

33:16.290 --> 33:18.490
will definitely get better and better.

33:18.900 --> 33:19.530
Okay?

33:20.980 --> 33:23.110
Don't be sad.

33:23.340 --> 33:23.730
Okay.

33:23.730 --> 33:24.860
Don't think about it.

33:24.860 --> 33:25.420
Alright.

33:25.530 --> 33:26.660
Everything will be fine.

33:26.660 --> 33:27.210
It will be fine.

33:27.210 --> 33:28.410
Things will work out!

33:28.420 --> 33:29.620
Things will work out!

33:34.620 --> 33:37.090
[Xie Lin]

33:44.670 --> 33:46.860
Where am I supposed to find this person?

33:46.860 --> 33:48.210
Should I just camp outside the Lyman Group

33:48.210 --> 33:49.210
every day?

33:51.660 --> 33:53.010
Xie Lin.

33:59.250 --> 34:01.380
Come with me to a wedding this weekend.

34:02.450 --> 34:03.250
Instead of finding that person,

34:03.250 --> 34:05.180
he actually plans to attend some wedding.

34:05.180 --> 34:06.140
The spectator frets

34:06.140 --> 34:07.340
more than the player.

34:19.739 --> 34:20.420
Mr. Xiao.

34:21.010 --> 34:23.270
Are you sure this navigation is correct?

34:23.380 --> 34:26.110
Who would hold a wedding
in the middle of nowhere?

34:30.170 --> 34:31.130
Now I understand

34:31.130 --> 34:32.699
why you asked me to come along.

34:32.699 --> 34:35.159
You're really treating me
like your driver.

34:53.340 --> 34:54.070
Don't worry.

34:54.219 --> 34:55.219
This is the place.

35:01.010 --> 35:02.300
The wedding is on the island.

35:02.300 --> 35:04.080
We need to take a boat
from the dock to get there.

35:04.080 --> 35:04.940
Then, Mr. Xiao,

35:04.940 --> 35:06.530
please tell me when it will end,

35:06.530 --> 35:08.260
so I'll schedule to pick you up.

35:09.150 --> 35:10.410
You're coming with me.

35:10.900 --> 35:11.860
What would I do there?

35:11.860 --> 35:13.920
I don't even know the bride and groom.

35:14.170 --> 35:15.130
You're my date.

35:27.970 --> 35:29.740
He really doesn't care

35:29.400 --> 35:35.270
♪ Life lays out the outline of my scenes ♪

35:29.740 --> 35:31.740
about being disqualified by Lyman?

35:33.970 --> 35:35.230
I didn't say anything.

35:36.150 --> 35:39.630
♪ The last act
was a monologue in a dream ♪

35:38.380 --> 35:40.010
How does that hotel look?

35:40.830 --> 35:44.600
♪ And in the next,
I wander through the city's noise ♪

35:41.380 --> 35:42.170
It's okay.

35:42.420 --> 35:43.220
I designed it.

35:45.750 --> 35:48.820
♪ So many arrivals
that turned out to be nothing ♪

35:47.530 --> 35:48.260
I didn't see it clearly just now.

35:48.260 --> 35:49.660
Let me take a closer look.

35:50.130 --> 35:51.000
Now I see it clearly.

35:50.250 --> 35:54.320
♪ I'm counting the beats of the clock ♪

35:51.420 --> 35:53.050
This is your design, Mr. Xiao.

35:53.050 --> 35:54.650
It's completely your style.

35:54.880 --> 35:58.820
♪ I can't tell which platform
is for leaving or returning ♪

35:56.090 --> 35:56.570
This...

35:56.900 --> 35:57.740
Am I seeing things?

35:57.740 --> 35:59.450
Why does it seem to be glowing?

35:59.490 --> 36:03.780
♪ Until you walk toward me ♪

35:59.650 --> 36:01.220
That's called sunlight reflection.

36:01.220 --> 36:02.680
This is called a metaphor.

36:04.700 --> 36:05.490
Exaggeration.

36:04.950 --> 36:10.150
♪ And my breath softens ♪

36:10.690 --> 36:15.890
♪ And fall into
this anticipation called "you" ♪

36:15.920 --> 36:20.640
♪ Because of you ♪

36:20.660 --> 36:27.430
♪ So you're beside the story
written by fate ♪

36:29.970 --> 36:31.420
♪ Oh, ok ♪

36:32.420 --> 36:33.840
♪ Oh, ok ♪

36:34.440 --> 36:35.700
♪ Oh, ok ♪

36:36.740 --> 36:38.740
♪ Oh, ok ♪

36:37.660 --> 36:38.990
Please come in, please.

36:39.090 --> 36:42.200
♪ Oh, ok, my love ♪

36:39.740 --> 36:40.740
This way, please.

36:41.780 --> 36:42.840
Welcome, Mr. Xiao.

36:43.260 --> 36:44.090
Congratulations, Mr. Wang.

36:43.340 --> 36:47.200
♪ It turns out you're my exception ♪

36:46.700 --> 36:47.700
This is...

36:48.820 --> 36:51.150
Hu Xiu, our studio's assistant designer.

36:51.650 --> 36:52.580
This is Mr. Wang,

36:52.590 --> 36:53.700
the owner of this island

36:53.700 --> 36:54.890
and the bride's father.

36:54.890 --> 36:56.490
Congratulations, Mr. Wang.

36:56.530 --> 36:57.380
Thank you.

36:57.380 --> 36:57.940
Welcome.

36:58.220 --> 36:59.420
Today's wedding

36:59.530 --> 37:01.700
is the hotel's first event
open to the public.

37:01.700 --> 37:03.360
I hope we can have a good start.

37:03.420 --> 37:04.420
Double happiness.

37:04.420 --> 37:05.170
It's a good thing.

37:05.170 --> 37:06.260
Thank you, Mr. Xiao.

37:06.260 --> 37:06.780
Please.

37:11.050 --> 37:11.900
Please move this signature board

37:11.900 --> 37:13.260
to the right.

37:14.450 --> 37:15.010
Yue.

37:15.820 --> 37:16.340
Dad.

37:16.530 --> 37:17.460
Mr. Xiao is here.

37:18.000 --> 37:18.770
Zhiyu.

37:19.450 --> 37:20.090
Well then,

37:20.130 --> 37:21.050
you young people chat,

37:21.050 --> 37:22.220
and I'll go attend to the other guests.

37:22.220 --> 37:22.740
Okay.

37:22.970 --> 37:23.860
Please go ahead.

37:23.860 --> 37:24.520
Sure thing.

37:26.170 --> 37:26.940
Zhiyu,

37:27.090 --> 37:28.300
I knew you'd come today,

37:28.300 --> 37:30.270
but I didn't expect you'd bring a date.

37:30.270 --> 37:31.230
Hello, Ms. Wang.

37:31.380 --> 37:32.940
I'm an assistant designer from Dynamism,

37:32.940 --> 37:33.450
Hu Xiu.

37:33.820 --> 37:34.220
Hello.

37:34.220 --> 37:35.280
Congratulations.

37:40.850 --> 37:41.710
Happy wedding.

37:41.740 --> 37:42.420
Thank you.

37:43.220 --> 37:45.130
The ceremony will be held here shortly.

37:45.130 --> 37:46.740
What do you think of everything arranged?

37:46.740 --> 37:47.300
I can see

37:47.300 --> 37:49.010
a lot of thought went into this.

37:49.010 --> 37:50.450
My husband prepared everything.

37:50.450 --> 37:52.510
I just gave random directions today.

37:52.880 --> 37:53.410
Oh right,

37:53.570 --> 37:55.430
you haven't met him yet, have you?

37:56.170 --> 37:56.900
Qiran,

37:56.970 --> 37:57.830
come over here.

38:18.940 --> 38:19.410
Hello.

38:19.530 --> 38:20.090
Hello.

38:20.220 --> 38:21.680
I was referred by Mr. Chen.

38:21.740 --> 38:23.000
My name is Zhang Qiran.

38:23.690 --> 38:24.730
I'm Hu Xiu.

38:47.340 --> 38:48.540
Wait a moment, Honey.

38:48.780 --> 38:49.910
Your strand of hair.

38:50.320 --> 38:51.720
Zhang Qiran, my husband.

38:52.300 --> 38:52.900
Qiran,

38:52.900 --> 38:54.700
this is my senior
from when I studied in America,

38:54.700 --> 38:56.900
and also the renowned architect
Xiao Zhiyu.

38:56.900 --> 38:57.530
I've heard so much about you.

38:57.530 --> 38:58.260
I often

38:58.450 --> 38:59.850
hear our Yue mention you.

39:00.220 --> 39:01.740
Finally get to meet you in person.

39:01.740 --> 39:02.870
Pleased to meet you.

39:10.090 --> 39:10.890
What's wrong?

39:12.610 --> 39:13.940
Is she feeling seasick?

39:14.380 --> 39:15.300
I'll go check on her.

39:15.300 --> 39:15.820
Okay.

39:18.610 --> 39:19.070
Qiran,

39:19.100 --> 39:20.710
let's greet other guests.

39:21.050 --> 39:21.490
Okay.

39:24.610 --> 39:25.260
Seasick?

39:29.650 --> 39:30.300
No.

39:31.270 --> 39:32.600
Just feeling nauseous.

39:35.820 --> 39:36.750
Long time no see.

39:36.890 --> 39:38.050
You look so cool today.

39:38.050 --> 39:38.910
Happy wedding.

39:38.970 --> 39:40.770
-Happy wedding.
-So beautiful.

39:46.420 --> 39:46.910
Mr. Xie.

39:46.940 --> 39:47.570
Mr. Wang.

39:48.090 --> 39:48.340
Welcome.

39:48.340 --> 39:49.570
Sorry to keep you waiting.

39:49.570 --> 39:50.450
Nice place.

39:50.940 --> 39:52.220
Take it easy for a moment.

39:52.220 --> 39:54.020
I need to take care of something.

39:59.220 --> 40:00.820
Facing the green mountains

40:02.170 --> 40:03.170
and clear waters.

40:04.130 --> 40:04.780
If you're free,

40:04.780 --> 40:07.740
you can come out and enjoy the view.

40:08.170 --> 40:08.900
Xie Lin.

40:10.780 --> 40:11.650
Qin.

40:14.220 --> 40:16.170
So you're the legendary

40:16.420 --> 40:17.420
junior Mr. Qin?

40:26.760 --> 40:27.400
Mr. Xie.

40:30.180 --> 40:31.010
You are?

40:31.530 --> 40:32.010
Hello.

40:32.260 --> 40:32.970
I am...

40:34.790 --> 40:35.490
Xiao Zhiyu.

40:36.570 --> 40:38.220
So you're Xiao Zhiyu.

40:40.010 --> 40:40.650
Mr. Xie,

40:41.050 --> 40:43.180
could I have a word with you in private?

40:43.820 --> 40:44.450
You see,

40:45.570 --> 40:48.230
young people nowadays
are so straightforward.

40:49.350 --> 40:51.380
I heard Mr. Xie values efficiency.

40:51.670 --> 40:52.380
As it happens,

40:52.380 --> 40:52.970
so do I.

40:54.800 --> 40:55.280
Good.

40:58.420 --> 40:59.060
Please.

41:25.090 --> 41:25.570
Uncle Chen,

41:25.570 --> 41:26.260
how have you been lately?

41:26.260 --> 41:27.940
This is Mr. Zheng.

41:27.940 --> 41:28.860
Let me introduce you.

41:28.860 --> 41:29.780
Just call me Zhang.

41:29.780 --> 41:30.090
Zhang.

41:30.090 --> 41:30.530
Ms. Hu.

41:30.530 --> 41:31.650
Shall we exchange contact information?

41:31.650 --> 41:32.260
Sure.

41:34.490 --> 41:35.700
Are you looking for Zhiyu?

41:35.700 --> 41:39.030
Your father-in-law and I
do business together frequently.

41:39.260 --> 41:41.820
My father said he went to chat
with Uncle Xie.

41:41.940 --> 41:43.200
He should be back soon.

41:43.570 --> 41:44.970
You can wait for him here.

41:46.860 --> 41:47.700
Ms. Wang,

41:48.650 --> 41:49.710
congratulations,

41:49.860 --> 41:50.610
really.

41:52.010 --> 41:52.820
Thank you.

41:53.530 --> 41:54.860
To be honest with you,

41:54.970 --> 41:57.450
I never thought I'd get married so early.

41:57.960 --> 42:00.560
I was actually
a bit afraid of marriage before.

42:02.130 --> 42:02.940
Indeed.

42:03.480 --> 42:06.530
A flash marriage, in particular,
requires more courage.

42:06.530 --> 42:07.490
Flash marriage?

42:08.500 --> 42:10.060
How do you know that?
